---
title: "onReport (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_decode: workflowId = metadata[0..32]
    q_decode --> q_check_zero: check workflowId
    q_check_zero --> q_error_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_zero --> q_check_allowlist: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_check_allowlist --> q_error_wf: !allowlisted(workflowId)
    q_error_wf --> [*]: revert WorkflowIdNotAllowlisted
    q_check_allowlist --> q_decode_report: allowlisted(workflowId)
    q_decode_report --> q_extract_selector: (target, data) = abi.decode(report)
    q_extract_selector --> q_check_selector: selector = data[0..4]
    q_check_selector --> q_check_target: !selectorAllowlisted(workflowId, target, selector)
    q_check_target --> q_error_target: !targetAllowlisted(workflowId, target)
    q_error_target --> [*]: revert TargetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_target --> q_error_sel: targetAllowlisted
    q_error_sel --> [*]: revert SelectorNotAllowlisted
    q_check_selector --> q_call: selectorAllowlisted
    q_call --> [*]: _call(target, data)

    note right of q_check_selector
        INV-001: Only allowlisted workflow+target+selector combinations can execute calls
        INV-002: Caller must have FORWARDER_ROLE and contract must not be paused
    end note
